HEADWORD: Suppalpation
<hw>Sup`pal*pa"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>suppalpari</ets> to caress a little; <ets>sub</ets> under, a little
+ <ets>palpare</ets> to caress.]</ety> <def>The act of enticing by soft
words; enticement.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

